data.description: This exceptional two-family brick home offers a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience. With its thoughtful design, high-end finishes, and a host of amenities, this property stands out as a unique opportunity for everyone. Step inside to discover a warm and inviting atmosphere, accentuated by the custom-made kitchen cabinets and top-of-the-line appliances, including a prestigious Sub-Zero refrigerator. The principal suite is a haven of tranquility, featuring ample storage space with its custom-made closets. Attention to detail is evident throughout, with high-quality finishes and fixtures enhancing the overall appeal of this lovely home. The long driveway, providing ample off-street parking, leads to a backyard paradise, designed for entertainment and relaxation. The above-ground swimming pool serves as the centerpiece of this private retreat, complemented by a bar area, perfect for hosting gatherings. Located in the heart of East Elmhurst, the property benefits from its proximity to a range of local amenities and services. You can even catch a glimpse of NYC's iconic skyrises from this elevated position atop the hill on 89th Street. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to public transportation, including the Q49 on Astoria Blvd and 90th St., and the Q33 on 23rd Ave and 89th St. Don't miss the chance to own this exceptional property, combining the best of urban living with a peaceful and private outdoor retreat!
